title: Sean Hayes
description: Samantha Bee sits down with actor, producer, and fellow podcaster Sean Hayes to discuss the movies they've never seen, bringing back celebrity poker tournaments, live theater, and plantar fasciitis and other medical issues she wants him to cover on his podcast HypocondriActor.
author: fullrelease@sambee.com (Samantha Bee & Earwolf)
